ck box.","pos":[3871,3944]},{"content":"This required step adds to the connection group the package entitlements that you configured earlier when you assigned packages to Active Directory groups.","pos":[3945,4100]},{"content":"App-V Server - PowerShell cmdlet","pos":[4165,4197]},{"content":"Use the following cmdlet, and specify the <ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;strong&gt;</ph>-Optional<ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ph> parameter:","pos":[4227,4306]},{"content":"Add-AppvServerConnectionGroupPackage","pos":[4322,4358]},{"content":"Syntax:","pos":[4383,4390]},{"content":"Example:","pos":[4640,4648]},{"content":"App-V Client on a Stand-alone computer","pos":[4849,4887]},{"content":"Create the connection group XML document, and set the <ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;strong&gt;</ph>Package<ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ph> tag attribute <ph id=\"ph3\">&lt;strong&gt;</ph>IsOptional<ph id=\"ph4\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ph> to <ph id=\"ph5\">&lt;strong&gt;</ph>“true”.","pos":[4926,5065]},{"content":"Use the following cmdlets to add and enable the connection group:","pos":[5091,5156]},{"content":"Add-AppvClientConnectionGroup","pos":[5173,5202]},{"content":"Enable-AppvClientConnectionGroup","pos":[5219,5251]},{"content":"Example connection group XML document with optional packages:","pos":[5289,5350]},{"pos":[5980,6178],"content":"Package PackageId=<ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;quot;</ph>fc6fe0f7-be3d-4643-b37d-fc3f62d4dd5c<ph id=\"ph2\">&amp;quot;\n</ph>   VersionId=<ph id=\"ph3\">&amp;quot;</ph>c67a71cd-3542-4a48-93e8-20c643c50970<ph id=\"ph4\">&amp;quot;\n</ph>   DisplayName=<ph id=\"ph5\">&amp;quot;</ph>Contoso Forms<ph id=\"ph6\">&amp;quot;\n</ph>   IsOptional=<ph id=\"ph7\">&amp;quot;</ph>false"},{"pos":[6196,6391],"content":"Package PackageId=<ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;quot;</ph>8f6301a5-4348-4039-9560-b27a5bb72711<ph id=\"ph2\">&amp;quot;\n</ph>   VersionId=<ph id=\"ph3\">&amp;quot;</ph>6c694b45-3e19-46c6-a327-d159aa39e1d2<ph id=\"ph4\">&amp;quot;\n</ph>   DisplayName=<ph id=\"ph5\">&amp;quot;</ph>Contoso Tax<